column3: A magician living in an abandoned theme park makes troubles disappear, and hope reappear, for a disenchanted teen enduring harsh relaties.
When a young boy vanishes, a small town uncovers a mystery involving secret experiments, terrifying supernatural forces an one strange little girl
At a high school full of unique characters, Tadano helps his shy and unsociable classmate Komi reach her goal of making firends with 100 people
